value.value: The only dorsal transverse muscle of embryonic/larval abdominal segments 1-7. It is an external muscle (Landgraf et al., 2003; Zarin and Labrador, 2019).

definition.value: No DT1 in thoracic segments, but one shown in A8 in Campos-Ortega and Hartenstein (1997).
